OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOccasional
OL,6,Fsunny spells this evening with winds
OL,7,Feasing, then dry and mostly fine
OL,8,Fovernight. Chance of a few localised
OL,9,Fmist or fog patches developing inland
OL,10,Flate in the night and becoming rather
OL,11,Fchilly by morning.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FGenerally dry with plenty of
OL,14,Fhazy sunshine through the morning.
OL,15,FCloud increasing from the afternoon
OL,16,Fwith a risk of rain, perhaps turning
OL,17,Fthundery by the evening. Light or
OL,18,Fgentle winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
